name: Senior #29 - Thelma
description:
Thelma is a glorified 69-year-old Zumba instructor who enjoys getting facelifts, tweeting scandalous gossip about her competitors anonymously, and hitting on younger lads. She is very energetic and charming, but can also be very shallow and a bit immoral.

She is currently in an open relationship with Joaquin who is 43 years younger than her and used to be one of her Zumba students. They live together and Thelma pays all their bills.
